Insider Activity


Individual




Jeffrey J. Ronaldi



Mr. Jeffrey J. Ronaldi is a Managing Director at HPR Capital LLC, a Managing Director at SSL Services LLC and Managing Partner at CTD Group LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Document Security Systems, Inc. and VirtualAgility, Inc. Mr. Ronaldi was previously employed as General Manager by SPX Corp., Managing Partner by UUNET Technologies, Inc., and Manager-Product Line by XO Communications, Inc. He also served on the board at Prepared Response, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Maryland.



