Jeffrey J. Ronaldi  CEO & Director, Document Security Systems, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships52$218,750As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Jeffrey J. Ronaldi, also known as Jeff, has been the Chief Executive Officer at Document Security Systems, Inc. since July 1, 2013. Mr. Ronaldi serves as General Manager of SPX Corporation's ImagExpo business. Mr. Ronaldi joined SPX Corporation in January 2003. His prior business experience includes positions at Mindsquared, LLC as managing partner, Newsletters.com as president & Chief Executive Officer and Concentric Networks (now, XO Communications) as product ... line manager. He has 25 years of experience driving revenues, market growth and profitability for start-up and high-growth companies such as Turtle Bay Technologies and Verizon. Mr. Ronaldi served as the Chief Executive Officer of DSS Technology Management, Inc. (alternate name, Lexington Technology Group, Inc.) since November 9, 2012 and also served same position since July 1, 2013. He also held sales, marketing and finance positions at UUNET Technologies (now WorldCom). He has been a Director of Document Security Systems, Inc. since July 1, 2013. He serves as a Director of VirtualAgility, Inc. He served as a Member of Advisory Board at DSS Technology Management, Inc. and served as its Director since July 1, 2013. He served as a Director of Prepared Response, Inc. Mr. Ronaldi holds a Bachelor of Science degree in Finance from the University of Maryland.Read Full Background




