               Company Size: $50 mil to less than $100 mil - Employee Range: 1,000 to less than 5,000. support.com is a new service, which provides consumers with "Instant Technology Relief" by quickly, conveniently and empathetically fixing your frustrating technology problems. By leveraging 10 years of experience solving the toughest computer problems for some of the world's largest companies, support.com is one of the easiest and time effective ways for consumers to handle computer issues. support.com will provide you with a free service estimate, with prices ranging from $29 to $99. Most importantly, we guarantee providing the highest level of customer service: If we can't resolve your problem, you don't pay.
Title: Chief Executive Officer
               Company: Document Security Systems Inc
Job Details
               Company Size: $10 mil to less than $25 mil - Employee Range: 100 to less than 500. Document Security Systems is a world leader in the development of optical deterrent technologies that help prevent counterfeiting and brand fraud from the use of the most advanced scanners, copiers and imaging systems in the market. The company's patented and patent-pending technologies protect valuable documents and printed products from counterfeiters and identity thieves. Document Security Systems' customers, which include international governments, major corporations and world financial institutions, use its covert and overt technologies to protect a number of applications including, but not limited to, currency, vital records, brand protection, ID Cards, internet commerce, passports and gift certificates. Document Security Systems' strategy is to become the world's leading producer of cutting-edge security technologies for paper, plastic and electronically generated printed assets.
